title: Ep. - 266 - 90 DAY FIANCE AND REAL HOUSEWIVES
description:
Rebecca Delgado-Smith, host of The Alarmist podcast helps Kate review 90 Day Fiance: The Other Way. From Ethiopia to Jordan, India to Mexico, this show is about six Americans leaving their families to move abroad.

 

New Orleans native Jonathan Lamb from Dating Around on Netflix explains what happened on his television blind date, and what he thinks about all of the hairstyles of the Real Housewives.

 

 


Reality Life with Kate Casey
